{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":7},{"title":2,"author":3,"date":4,"citation":5,"uri":6},"Sicile","Orsi","1896","\u003Cspan>Paolo Orsi, « Sicile », \u003Ci>Bulletin de Correspondance Hellénique\u003C/i> 20 (1896): 399‑400\u003C/span>","https://www.zotero.org/groups/isicily/items/FWX5CWBN",[8,110,164,237,289,341],{"file":9,"uri":9,"title":10,"status":11,"editionAuthor":13,"type":14,"objectType":18,"material":22,"condition":26,"layoutDesc":27,"handNote":34,"date":48,"places":53,"geo":62,"provenance":55,"provenanceGeo":66,"country":69,"region":70,"settlement":71,"repository":72,"idno":76,"textLang":79,"tmNumber":26,"letterHeights":83,"publications":84,"zotero":88,"keywords":92,"html":103,"bibl":104},"ISic001869","Funerary inscription for Artemo",{"_":12},"edited",null,{"_":15,"ana":16,"ref":17},"funerary","#function.funerary","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html",{"_":19,"ana":20,"ref":21},"block","#object.block","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/189.html",{"_":23,"ana":24,"ref":25},"limestone","#material.stone.limestone","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html","",{"layout":28},{"p":29,"rs":30,"damage":26},"Three lines of Greek letters, seemingly not centered / regularly laid out.",{"_":31,"ana":32,"ref":33},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":35,"dimensions":36},"Described by Orsi (1896) as 'scritto a pessimi caratteri', and (1899) as 'lettere cattive, rustiche cosi che a tutta prima sembrano archaiche, e molto sconservate... L'iscrizione negligentemente redatta e scolpita è funebre di tarda età'. Pace states 'lettere del III sec. av. Cr.', but given the presence of lunate epsilon and Orsi's comments, a later date seems much more likely.",[37,44],{"type":38,"l":39,"from":40,"to":41,"h":42,"unit":43},"letterHeight","Line 1-3","line1","line3","55-95","mm",{"type":45,"l":46,"from":40,"to":47,"unit":43},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","line2",{"_":49,"notBefore":50,"notAfter":51,"evidence":52},"Suggested to be of later Roman date by Orsi on the basis of lettering etc.",101,400,"lettering",[54,58],{"_":55,"type":56,"ref":57},"Kamarina","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462126",{"_":59,"type":60,"ref":61},"Santa Croce Camerina","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/6540853",[63],[64,65],36.8736,14.4507,[67,68],36.8759983,14.4377781,"Italy","Sicily","Siracusa",{"_":73,"role":74,"ref":75},"Museo Archeologico Regionale Paolo Orsi","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/097",{"_":77,"type":78},"16474","inventory",{"_":80,"mainLang":81,"languages":82},"Ancient Greek","grc",[80],[],[85,86,87],"Orsi, 1896, Sicile","Orsi, 1899, Camarina (Campagna archeologica del 1896)","Pace, 1927, Camarina: topografia, storia, archeologia",[89,90,91],"FWX5CWBN","ICW2M9P2","ZJ6KUFMM",[93,94,95,15,19,23,96,97,98,99,100,101,102,81],"isic001869","funerary inscription for artemo",{"_":12},"kamarina","santa croce camerina","italy","sicily","siracusa","museo archeologico regionale paolo orsi","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρτεμοι\n                    Ἀρτεμιδό\n                    του\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀρτεμοι\">Ἀρτεμοι̣\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἀρτεμιδό\n                    του\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἀρτεμιδό\n                    του\">Ἀρτεμιδό \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>τ̣ου\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Csp